Smith was well known for wearing a turban.
He stated that the turban had no religious significance and was something he had worn since he was young.

Matt Collar of AllMusic suggested the turban was a theatrical gesture to his spiritual views on music, but Smith himself said he did not know why he started wearing a turban and referenced the iconic headwear of Sun Ra and Sonny Rollins' mohawk.
